    </section><section id="fs-id2687518" class="problems-exercises"><title>Problems Exercise</title><exercise id="fs-id3245705" type="problems-exercises">
      <problem id="fs-id3035351">
        <para id="import-auto-id2424366">(a) A 22.0 kg child is riding a playground merry-go-round that is rotating at 40.0 rev/min. What centripetal force must she exert to stay on if she is 1.25 m from its center? </para>
    <para id="import-auto-id789255">(b) What centripetal force does she need to stay on an amusement park merry-go-round that rotates at 3.00 rev/min if she is 8.00 m from its center? </para>
